title: "Video Games Improve Intelligence!" 🤔️  SCIENCE CAN LIE.
description:
Some people say video games improve your memory, some people say they improve rapid decision making, some say they improve your intelligence.  Science can lie, and in the format of a youtube video, it's very easy for doctors to appear to be giving a reasonable summary of a research paper whereas, in fact, they're misrepresenting it, cherry-picking, or simply lying.
